    Our mission is to
    Make energy accessible

    Established in 1990, MEIL is an ISO 9001:2015 certified leader in manufacturing CRGO products and manufacturing transformers. We are approved by Power Grid Corporation of India Limited for 400 kV Class Projects.

    We are processors of CRGO Slit Coils, Cut Laminations, Wound Core & Windings, Amorphous Core, CRGO Core Assembly & CRGO Core Coil Assembly, serving around the world electrical industry with unparalleled expertise and innovation.

    Our Journey Through Time:
    The Story Behind Our Legacy

    From humble beginnings to industry leadership, our journey is a testament to innovation, dedication, and a relentless pursuit of excellence. Each milestone we achieve adds to the legacy we've built over the years.

    1990

    Humble Beginning

    Mangal Electrical Industries was founded and begin its journey in transformer industry.

    2008

    First Milestone

    Established our transformer plant, became Pvt. Ltd., and completed our first CRGO lamination & billing on April 22, 2008.

    2012

    First Amorphous Billing

    Completed our first Amorphous Core Transformer billing, advancing energy-efficient solutions.

    2013

    Expansion to Reengus

    Established the Reengus plant to boost production capacity and meet growing industry demands.

    2014

    Acquisition of Powertech SEZ

    Acquired the Powertech SEZ plant to enhance manufacturing capabilities and expand operational strength.

    2015

    Major Milestones and Growth

    Exported to DDPL, earned ISO 9001:2015 & ISO 14001:2015, set up a VKI unit, and launched our EPC Division.

    2016

    ICB Manufacturing Initiated

    Commenced the production of Insulated Core Blocks (ICB), expanding our product portfolio and technological capabilities.

    2017

    First ICB Billing

    Achieved our first billing for Insulated Core Blocks (ICB), marking a new milestone in our manufacturing journey.

    2021

    132kV Project Success

    Delivered the 132kV project for PGCIL, showcasing high-voltage expertise, and achieved ISO 9001:2015 registration.

    2022

    ISO 14001:2015 Certification

    Achieved ISO 14001:2015, strengthening our commitment to environmental management and sustainability.

    2023

    ZED Silver Certification

    Received ZED Silver approval, reflecting our dedication to excellence in manufacturing and operational practices.

    2024

    Transition to Public Limited

    Transitioned from a Private Limited to a Public Limited company, marking a significant step in our growth journey.

    What does Mangal Electrical Industries Ltd. specialise in?
    Mangal Electrical Industries Ltd. specialises in manufacturing transformer components such as CRGO Slit Coils, CRGO Cut Laminations, CRGO Core Assemblies, Wound Cores, Amorphous Cores, and Immersed Circuit Breakers.
    Where are you located?
    Our headquarters are located at C-61, Road No 1 C Vishwa Karma Industrial Area, Jaipur Rajasthan.
    What certifications do you have?
    We are ISO 9001:2015 certified, ensuring our commitment to quality and customer satisfaction. Also, we have other certifications like - NABL certificate for our CRGO testing lab, NTPC certification, and Approval for the 400 kV class from PGCIL.
    Who are some of your notable clients?
    Our notable clients include NTPC, PGCIL, ADANI, Renew Power, and AVADA.
    Do you offer custom manufacturing services?
    Yes, we provide custom engineering solutions to meet specific requirements for transformer components.
    How can I request a quote?
    You can request a quote by contacting us through our website's contact form or by calling our customer service team.
